get some sleep.

11:54.000 --> 11:58.880
I just found out the client's
coming in tomorrow at 3:00 for an update.

11:59.770 --> 12:01.900
-Oh,crap.
-What?

12:01.900 --> 12:06.620
Did we ever get my suit pants fixed
after the cuff came unraveled at christmas?

12:07.060 --> 12:09.730
