to look for a job.

12:29.580 --> 12:32.090
hey... there is a tailor

12:32.090 --> 12:36.640
who works at the mall by city hall
who does alterations while you wait.

12:36.640 --> 12:40.820
I can drop them off first thing
and pick them up at lunch.

12:43.930 --> 12:47.480
On second thought,
bring those brains of yours over here.

12:47.860 --> 12:50.180
I think I do feel
like kissing them.

13:03.100 --> 13:04.920
No,I just felt him there,

13:04.920 --> 13:08.450
and he was standing over my bed,
just looming there.

13:08.450 --> 13:12.170
And then he leaned down...
and then he kissed me.

13:17.210 --> 13:19.850
you'd better not be playing
solitaire on that computer.

13:19.850 --> 13:22.320
It's almost 2:00.
You're cutting it close.

13:23.100 --> 13:24.310
You're welcome.

13:24.310 --> 13:27.500
I'm sorry. There was a thank you in there.
You just didn't hear it.

13:27.500 --> 13:30.290
Well,you're right.
I'm running late.

13:33.350 --> 13:36.060
The strangest thing happened
to me on the way over here.

13:36.060 --> 13:38.150
I saw this woman.

13:38.690 --> 13:43.010
She looked just like that girl i've been seeing
in my dreams--the one who keeps getting kissed?

13:43.010 --> 13:46.010
She was going up an escalator.
I was going down.

14:00.640 --> 14:02.320
Geez.

14:02.320 --> 14:06.570
