two to three hours.

17:32.330 --> 17:35.650
My friend finally had to leave.
I'm missing a day's work.

17:36.260 --> 17:39.350
You know what? I work with one
of the detectives here.

17:39.350 --> 17:41.670
Let me see if I can't get him
to talk to you.

17:41.670 --> 17:43.890
Oh,thanks. That would be great.

17:53.850 --> 17:55.350
I'm sorry,miss...?

17:55.350 --> 17:56.620
Walsh.

17:56.620 --> 17:59.210
Kathleen walsh.
I'm not married.

17:59.210 --> 18:02.360
Mrs. Dubois explained you've been waiting
a long while.What can we help you with?

18:02.360 --> 18:05.410
Well,I should tell you,
I called the police yesterday morning.

18:05.410 --> 18:06.730
They came by
my house,but...

18:06.730 --> 18:09.170
start from the beginning.
Tell us what happened.

18:10.230 --> 18:12.460
Six months ago,i
moved to phoenix--

18:12.460 --> 18:15.440
just before the start of the school year.
I teach music.

18:16.350 --> 18:20.520
Anyway,I found this wonderful apartment
for very little money.

18:21.410 --> 18:25.350
But shortly after i settled in,
I began to hear noises...

18:25.350 --> 18:27.010
only at night.

18:27.010 --> 18:29.910
They'd start just as I was
getting ready for bed.

18:34.060 --> 18:35.360
Do you have any pets?

18:35.360 --> 18:38.020
A cat-- boots.

18:39.050 --> 18:42.110
But I've had him,like,forever.
He doesn't make these sounds.

18:42.110 --> 18:44.140
Okay,so you heard
there sounds...

18:44.140 --> 18:47.090
yeah. I would call out,
but no one would answer.

18:47.090 --> 18:49.040
Uh,this would happen...

18:49.040 --> 18:51.470
like,three,maybe
four times a week.

18:51.470 --> 18:52.920
So what'd you do?

18:52.920 --> 18:55.670
I didn't think that there was
anything to do.

18:55.670 --> 18:58.630
I wasn't certain that
there was anything really there...

18:58.940 --> 19:01.840
so frankly,for a long
time,I did nothing.

19:02.060 --> 19:04.270
But then the noises
started to change.

19:04.270 --> 19:06.460
What do you mean? Change how?

19:07.020 --> 19:09.500
Well,there was
this clicking sound.

19:09.500 --> 19:10.890
Clicking?

19:15.360 --> 19:17.480
-a camera.
-Huh?

19:17.480 --> 19:20.520
I was wondering if you thought
it sounded like a camera.

19:22.290 --> 19:24.170
Um... I don't know.

19:24.170 --> 19:26.750
Okay. Whatever it was,
there's this new sound.

19:26.750 --> 19:29.440
And I ignored that
for a while,too.

19:29.440 --> 19:31.900
But then two
nights ago...

19:31.900 --> 19:34.080
I felt him there...

19:34.380 --> 19:36.140
close.

19:36.410 --> 19:38.790
He was standing
over the bed.

19:39.730 --> 19:42.700
Forgive me for asking,but how do you
know that?How do you know he was there?

19:51.110 --> 19:53.240
Stand up.

19:53.870 --> 19:55.070
Excuse me?

19:55.070 --> 19:57.310
Would you stand up,please?

20:01.310 --> 20:03.230
Close your eyes.

20:15.450 --> 20:17.480
Any questions?

20:19.230 --> 20:20.710
No.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.810
and then?

20:39.510 --> 20:41.610
He kissed me.

20:44.010 --> 20:45.670
So what'd you do?

20:45.670 --> 20:47.630
I screamed.

20:48.050 --> 20:49.980
And then he was gone.

20:49.980 --> 20:52.350
And then i
called the police,

20:52.350 --> 20:55.160
and then the police came over.
And then--

20:55.160 --> 20:57.450
I have no way
of proving this...

20:57.980 --> 20:59.820
but I think they
laughed at me.

20:59.820 --> 21:02.370
Whoa,hold it,you're...
I want to make sure i've got this right.

21:02.370 --> 21:06.130
You're not alleging that this guy raped you,
struck you,fondled you?

21:06.580 --> 21:09.070
A man broke into my apartment...

21:09.410 --> 21:11.270
and he kissed me.

21:14.160 --> 21:14.860
miss walsh...

21:14.860 --> 21:17.210
you're going to tell me
to change the locks,

21:17.210 --> 21:19.340
move in with a friend...

21:20.080 --> 21:21.900
