for help.

21:42.920 --> 21:44.580
Victimized?

21:44.580 --> 21:46.810
A man keeps breaking
into her apartment.

21:46.810 --> 21:48.800
-Maybe.
-No. Not maybe.

21:48.800 --> 21:50.190
