23:01.140 --> 23:03.210
Uh,never mind. No big deal.

23:03.210 --> 23:05.300
I've conferred with mrs. Dubois here

23:05.300 --> 23:09.750
and we've decided to post a visible
police presence right outside your building.

23:09.750 --> 23:13.830
They'll be there 24 hours a day,
and if anyone comes in or out,they'll see it.

23:13.830 --> 23:16.990
Additionally,we'll set up
a direct phone link to your apartment.

23:17.420 --> 23:20.000
If anyone does come in,
you just pick up that phone and we're there.

23:21.570 --> 23:23.240
Wow. That's great.

23:23.240 --> 23:26.970
I was just hoping that maybe you could
send someone over to take a second look.

23:27.740 --> 23:29.480
Really?

23:31.390 --> 23:33.310
I wouldn't hear of it.

23:33.310 --> 23:36.170
This kissing thing,
that's not something i want to play around with.

23:36.170 --> 23:37.970
Well,thank you.

23:40.530 --> 23:42.450
And thank you,mrs. Dubois.

23:42.450 --> 23:45.630
Oh,no,it's nothing.
That's what we're here for.

23:45.630 --> 23:48.520
Absolutely.
That is what we're here for.

23:54.260 --> 23:55.610
Hello?

23:57.310 --> 23:59.140
Hello?

24:00.690 --> 24:02.830
Are you here?

24:05.520 --> 24:07.720
Are you watching me?

24:11.610 --> 24:12.940
hey.

24:13.910 --> 24:17.220
You're home,
and it's not even 12:00.

24:19.270 --> 24:21.700
Will wonders never cease?

24:21.700 --> 24:24.620
you'd almost think
that I lived here.

24:28.790 --> 24:30.610
I missed you.

24:30.860 --> 24:35.750
I hate waking up and having dreams
and not having you to share them with.

24:36.700 --> 24:37.970
Well,good.

24:37.970 --> 24:40.830
Because I suspect
that pretty soon,

24:41.500 --> 24:44.380
not only will i be around during the
middle of the night,

24:44.380 --> 24:47.600
but quite possibly
during the day,as well.

24:48.770 --> 24:50.560
What are you talking about?

24:50.560 --> 24:53.190
Well,we went to
see the client today,

24:53.190 --> 24:56.050
and it's like
i was invisible.

24:56.050 --> 24:58.790
Nobody really wanted
to hear from me.

24:58.790 --> 25:02.790
It was the edrick show.
All day,all the time.

25:05.230 --> 25:08.030
You know,the guy's been an
engineer for 15 minutes,

25:08.030 --> 25:11.510
but it's like he's galileo the way they
hang on his every word.

25:12.450 --> 25:13.540
Honey...

25:13.540 --> 25:15.410
and not just...

25:17.000 --> 25:19.150
not just the client,

25:19.150 --> 25:22.700
but the senior guys
from our frm,as well.

25:22.700 --> 25:24.770
I know thaok.

25:24.770 --> 25:26.780
I used to get
that look.

25:26.780 --> 25:29.950
That's the "you're the
future of this company" look.

25:30.720 --> 25:33.540
Hmm,I think you're exaggerating.
I met edrick.

25:33.540 --> 25:36.520
He bows at your feet.
He worships you.

25:36.520 --> 25:39.080
He's got me lined up
in his crosshairs.

25:39.890 --> 25:42.310
he covets my
parking space.

25:42.870 --> 25:47.920
He lusts after the senior
vice president nameplate on my office door.

25:49.150 --> 25:52.440
He pines for my four extra
vacation days a year.

25:54.930 --> 25:57.880
And you know what the
surprising part is

26:00.200 --> 26:02.720
I don't think i
really give a damn.

26:05.030 --> 26:07.200
It's good to be home.

26:10.430 --> 26:11.890
And you?

26:11.890 --> 26:14.060
Any more kissing dreams?

26:14.500 --> 26:17.900
Mm,the kissing has stopped.
There is no kissing.

26:19.200 --> 26:22.210
No real clarity,either.

26:37.530 --> 26:39.540
interview elkin again?

26:40.080 --> 26:42.490
-Whatever for?
-I've been having these dreams.

26:42.560 --> 26:44.080
Allison...

26:44.930 --> 26:47.010
all of them are very similar.

26:47.010 --> 26:51.040
Up until last night,I thought they were
about this blind woman,kathleen walsh,

26:51.040 --> 26:55.120
being kissed by a man who has no features,
being kissed by sam elkin.

26:55.850 --> 26:58.900
But then last night,
I had the same dream,

26:58.900 --> 27:02.980
set in the same place,
but kathleen is gone.

27:04.440 --> 27:07.880
Elkin's dead girlfriend,
amanda crane,is in her place.

27:07.880 --> 27:09.400
And this suggests?

27:09.400 --> 27:11.760
I don't know,but I'd like
to try and find out.

27:13.740 --> 27:16.640
I don't have it,
and I couldn't do it.

27:17.100 --> 27:19.690
I left here at 10:30 last night.

27:19.690 --> 27:23.560
No matter how much I try,
I can't design with my eyes closed.

27:24.240 --> 27:27.820
The drawings,the silicone diode--
I don't have them,I'm still working on them.

27:28.320 --> 27:30.140
Sorry,kid.

27:32.640 --> 27:34.320
I need your help.

27:35.410 --> 27:36.970
Excuse me?

27:36.970 --> 27:38.200
All my work.

27:38.200 --> 27:41.930
I sent it down to qc,
double-check the specs.

27:42.670 --> 27:44.800
None of it checked out.

27:44.800 --> 27:47.700
The quality control guys
called it gibberish.

27:52.900 --> 27:56.810
It's only a matter of time
before everyone upstairs hears about it.

28:01.210 --> 28:03.350
I need your help,mr. Dubois.

28:20.470 --> 28:21.860
so what'd I do?

28:21.860 --> 28:24.150
Well,that's what I was hoping
to figure out.

28:25.640 --> 28:28.710
I don't know if you remember me.
My name's allison dubois.

28:28.710 --> 28:30.830
I work with
the district attorney's office.

28:30.830 --> 28:34.820
I was here for your parole hearing the
other day. Sat right over there.

28:36.180 --> 28:38.580
You waiting for a thank you?

28:39.510 --> 28:41.860
It's gonna be a long wait.

28:44.120 --> 28:46.350
Well,no,I'm not here
for a thank you.

28:46.350 --> 28:49.820
I'd just like
to get some questions answered.

28:49.820 --> 28:53.090
Well,I don't know.
Depends on the questions.

28:53.550 --> 28:55.750
I mean,what's in it for me?

28:56.300 --> 28:59.120
Looks like I'm gonna be in here
the rest of my life.

28:59.120 --> 29:02.250
I'm not what you'd call
highly incentivized.

29:02.660 --> 29:05.310
Okay,well,let's start
with an easy one then.

29:05.310 --> 29:08.340
Why did you sit
there the other day

29:08.340 --> 29:11.480
and plead forgiveness
for a crime that you didn't commit?

29:13.610 --> 29:15.990
I mean,I know your
lawyer must have told you

29:15.990 --> 29:20.910
your only chance of parole was for you to come in and
sit there and tell the board what they wanted to hear,

29:21.510 --> 29:23.920
but I'm here to tell you,

29:23.920 --> 29:28.380
I strongly suspect that you
did not commit that crime.

29:29.760 --> 29:32.650
Now,I'm not on the board,and I'm with
the district attorney's office,

29:32.650 --> 29:36.470
but I'm no attorney,
so I can't really promise you anything.

29:37.080 --> 29:39.710
But if you have a story to tell,

29:39.710 --> 29:42.310
I would like to hear it.

29:42.310 --> 29:44.610
And if I believe you,

29:45.340 --> 29:49.440
I will do everything I can
to be sure that everyone listens.

29:54.160 --> 29:56.480
I loved amanda crane.

29:57.710 --> 30:01.170
She was a college girl,
I was a guy who fixed cars.

30:02.630 --> 30:04.690
Her friends didn't think
much of me.

30:04.690 --> 30:07.010
Her family didn't think
much of me.

30:07.010 --> 30:09.150
But I loved her.

30:09.700 --> 30:12.260
We went together for months.

30:12.760 --> 30:15.630
Used to spend almost
every day together.

30:16.370 --> 30:19.190
Every day except tuesdays.

30:20.260 --> 30:23.010
At first,she was always
coming up with excuses.

30:23.010 --> 30:26.180
I have a test,
I have a paper due.

30:26.760 --> 30:29.170
Then she switched her story
on me.

30:29.170 --> 30:32.410
Said she had a job,
she had to work.

30:32.980 --> 30:35.090
Didn't really bother me
at first.

30:35.090 --> 30:37.490
Didn't think much of it.

30:37.930 --> 30:41.890
Then I lost my wallet one night,
had no money to get home.

30:41.890 --> 30:45.680
I went over to her dorm,
she wasn't there.

30:45.680 --> 30:48.220
It was:00 in the morning.

30:48.220 --> 30:51.390
Next day she tells me
she was working all night.

30:51.390 --> 30:53.900
"Doing what?" I said.

30:54.630 --> 30:57.280
That's when things started
to get strange.

30:58.040 --> 31:01.730
For a while,she wouldn't tell me,
but I wouldn't let it go.

31:02.530 --> 31:05.170
I was like a dog with a bone.

31:05.690 --> 31:08.410
Finally,one night,
she tells me.

31:09.250 --> 31:11.340
She met a man.

31:12.820 --> 31:15.640
He offered to pay her way
through school.

31:15.640 --> 31:18.730
All she had to do was go over
to this apartment he owned.

31:18.730 --> 31:22.840
When she gets inside,
she puts on a blindfold,spends the night.

31:23.180 --> 31:25.540
-And do what?
-Exactly.

31:25.540 --> 31:27.600
That's what I wanted to know.

31:27.600 --> 31:30.070
She swears to me,
she's not doing anything.

31:30.070 --> 31:34.930
She just puts on a blindfold,takes off
her clothes,puts on a nightgown,goes to bed.

31:35.500 --> 31:37.370
Got up the next morning,

31:37.370 --> 31:41.840
put her clothes back on,took the
blindfold off,and walked out the door.

31:43.260 --> 31:45.190
And that was it?

31:45.890 --> 31:48.080
So she said.

31:49.790 --> 31:51.570
I asked her if he was there.

31:51.570 --> 31:54.360
She said she supposed so,
but she never heard him,

31:54.360 --> 31:58.490
never felt him,
never sensed he was there.

31:59.310 --> 32:01.980
I didn't believe her at first.

32:02.520 --> 32:06.750
I used to drop her off a couple of
blocks away.She'd let me use the car.

32:08.960 --> 32:11.010
Then one night,I followed her.

32:12.830 --> 32:15.260
She caught me
before she got there.

32:15.800 --> 32:17.260
She was furious.

32:17.260 --> 32:19.940
We had a huge fight,
broke up.

32:21.390 --> 32:23.580
I'd call her,
she wouldn't answer.

32:23.580 --> 32:26.780
I'd go over to her dorm,
she wouldn't let me in.

32:27.660 --> 32:30.790
That's when she got
the restraining order.

32:31.870 --> 32:34.940
I stayed away
for a month,

32:35.660 --> 32:37.870
but then I couldn't
take it any longer.

32:37.870 --> 32:40.270
I went over to her dorm.

32:40.270 --> 32:42.190
damn near busted the door down.

32:42.190 --> 32:46.220
Her roommate threatened to call the cops,
but amanda finally let me in.

32:46.870 --> 32:51.140
Roommate took off,
and we had another huge fight

32:52.290 --> 32:54.640
and then,a huge cry...

32:56.460 --> 32:59.140
and then,we made love.

33:02.360 --> 33:05.370
I told her I was going to find
a way to pay for school.

33:05.370 --> 33:07.820
I was going to do it.

33:08.320 --> 33:11.540
She told me she loved me,
she missed me.

33:12.070 --> 33:16.030
She was going to quit.She was going to
find a way to tell that guy that night.

33:19.530 --> 33:22.160
That was the last time
i saw her.

33:25.920 --> 33:29.180
Next thing I know,they found
her car at that car wash.

33:29.730 --> 33:34.070
My dna was everywhere.
It was inside the car,inside her.

33:35.890 --> 33:38.850
I told them my story,
but no one believed me.

33:41.300 --> 33:42.580
Ma'am?

33:43.080 --> 33:45.150
What are you thinking?

33:45.150 --> 33:48.650
I was thinking,have you
ever met kathleen walsh?

33:49.330 --> 33:52.160
No,I don't think so.
What does she look like?

33:53.800 --> 33:57.500
I'm thinking she looks a lot
like this guy's next victim.

33:59.810 --> 34:02.180
so what you are saying is that
there's this man

34:02.180 --> 34:04.440
who likes to watch women sleep?

34:04.440 --> 34:07.200
I'm not going to even pretend
to know what he likes.

34:07.200 --> 34:10.730
You think this is the guy who's been sneaking
into your friend kathleen's apartment?

34:10.730 --> 34:12.880
Well,she's not my friend,
but yes,

34:12.880 --> 34:17.210
what I'm saying is i feel very strongly the man
who's been watching kathleen is the same man

34:17.210 --> 34:19.800
who was watching elkin's
girlfriend,amanda,

34:19.800 --> 34:22.409
and very well may have been
responsible for her death.

34:22.409 --> 34:26.610
You know,when I was preparing for elkin's
parole hearing,I remember reading his statement.

34:26.610 --> 34:29.960
This crazy story about
his girlfriend having a job,

34:29.960 --> 34:32.710
only he didn't know where,
and he didn't know with whom.

34:32.710 --> 34:35.080
-I know,it sounds so bizarre.
-Bizarre?

34:35.610 --> 34:38.280
no,it aspires to "bizarre."

34:39.590 --> 34:43.310
allison,this man's sperm was still
inside her when they found the body.

34:43.310 --> 34:47.510
Yeah,they made up the night before.
He went by her dorm.Her roommate saw him.

34:47.510 --> 34:50.909
Precisely,he was in violation of the restraining
order she took out against him.

34:50.909 --> 34:54.989
Not exactly the kind of thing you want to put
in front of a judge in hopes of reopening a case.

34:55.610 --> 34:57.520
What if we could catch him?

34:57.520 --> 34:58.980
You lost me.

34:58.980 --> 35:01.300
Well,we know he likes kathleen.

35:01.300 --> 35:05.130
