just took over.

41:51.300 --> 41:54.320
Well,I'm just happy to know
he's behind bars.

41:54.320 --> 41:57.900
Which reminds me,there is someone
who would very much like to meet you.

42:09.170 --> 42:10.610
Kathleen.

42:12.560 --> 42:14.370
This is sam elkin.

42:15.230 --> 42:17.530
It's very nice to meet you.

42:18.230 --> 42:20.270
Nice to meet you,sam.

42:22.570 --> 42:26.540
I've never slept with an executive senior
vice president before.

42:26.540 --> 42:29.950
Five extra vacation
days a year.

42:30.980 --> 42:32.920
Very impressive.

